@startuml
title LogSys - ReadLogs Sequence (Filtered Query)

actor Client
participant LogManager
participant LogReader
database Backend as "File / SQLite"

Client -> LogManager: ReadLogs(level, filter)
activate LogManager
LogManager -> LogReader: Read(level, filter)
activate LogReader
LogReader -> Backend: query matching level + filter (Since/Until/Contains)
Backend --> LogReader: raw rows / lines
LogReader -> LogReader: deserialize into []LogEntry
LogReader --> LogManager: []LogEntry
deactivate LogReader
LogManager --> Client: []LogEntry
deactivate LogManager

@enduml
